          <%= _("You have the <strong>right</strong> to request information " \
                "from any publicly-funded body, and get answers. " \
                "{{site_name}} helps you make a Freedom of Information " \
                "request. It also publishes all requests online.",
                :site_name => site_name) %>
        </p>
      </div>
